**Summary:** The Attribution API sends attribution campaign events using advertising identifiers (idfa, idfv, adid, android_app_set_id) to track install attribution, with events held for 72 hours for user matching before being dropped if no matching user is found.

**Keywords:**
- Attribution API
- advertising identifiers
- idfa (Identifier for Advertiser)
- idfv (Identifier for Vendor) 
- adid (Google ADID)
- android_app_set_id
